description: Lists details about all member accounts for the current GuardDuty administrator account.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The unique ID of the detector that is associated with the member. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The ID of the member account.

nested_items.name: DetectorId
nested_items.description: The detector ID of the member account.

nested_items.name: Email
nested_items.description: The email address of the member account.

nested_items.name: RelationshipStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the relationship between the member and the administrator.

nested_items.name: InvitedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the invitation was sent.

nested_items.name: UpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The last-updated timestamp of the member.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination parameter to be used on the next list operation to retrieve more items.
